collaboration001.title: Holiday Hideouts
collaboration001.shortDescription: A comprehensive full-stack web application that provides a seamless platform for users to discover and book holiday homes. It offers an intuitive search interface and a secure booking system.

collaboration002.title: Tic Tac Toe
collaboration002.shortDescription: A simple implementation of Tic Tac Toe. Two players take turns marking spaces in a 3x3 grid, aiming to place three marks in a row horizontally, vertically, or diagonally. The game's status updates dynamically as the game progresses.
